, soup recipes, recipes.";i:68;s:96:"Minestrone is a thick, mixed vegetable soup using almost any combination of seasonal vegetables.";i:69;s:88:"Add vegetable broth to pot, plus drained tomatoes, beans, carrot, hot water, and spices.";i:70;s:82:"I made up a big pot yesterday and it was so tasty, i think leftovers are in order.";i:71;s:46:"Short cuts of pasta or rice may also be added.";i:72;s:125:"This soup is made all in one pan, is full of all sorts of veggies and even pasta, all in a delicious rich tomato based broth.";i:73;s:30:"Now, just remove the bay leaf.";i:74;s:88:"Add vegetable broth to pot, plus drained tomatoes, beans, carrot, hot water, and spices.";i:75;s:71:"Heat two tablespoons of olive oil over medium heat in a large soup pot.";}}